{"tid":1703743,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"街坊家中拍片 遭警射胡椒彈","createTime":"2019-11-10T11:58:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-10T12:12:48.000Z","uid":25558,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"6d636997ac315e9acec2ba9efbc7a2af5194e52a","tid":1703743,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T11:58:23.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20191110/U5GPBGPBQU32VHIY65LSLILY6U/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20191110%2FU5GPBGPBQU32VHIY65LSLILY6U%2F&d=Fs4PzESj5DMZecC7Kr%2FqWM5Q2JFdPMmcxM5Tq6mQO7A%3D&h=1b7e135b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20191110%2FU5GPBGPBQU32VHIY65LSLILY6U%2F&h=b5f87030\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20191110/U5GPBGPBQU32VHIY65LSLILY6U/</a><br />\n<br />\n街坊家中拍片 遭警射胡椒彈<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】警方昨凌晨在將軍澳區清場期間多次進出富康花園，截查多名街坊，對居民造成極大滋擾。有居民在家中發現防暴警在樓下截查三名年輕人，遂從窗戶拍攝地面情況，竟然遭警員粗暴喝止，並先後向窗口發射四次胡椒球彈阻嚇，事主面部「中椒」。蘇姓事主兒子昨受訪談及防暴警向其家亂射胡椒彈時直斥警察離譜，不負責任。<br />\n<br />\n蘇先生與父母及外婆同住富康花園一個低層單位，他憶述事件經過稱，昨日凌晨3時一家人已入睡，突然樓下傳來嘈吵聲，其父親被吵醒從房間窗戶望下，見到一班防暴警追捕年輕人，並截停三人查問，其父親見狀取出手機拍攝，「諗住保護啲年輕人」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://appledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com/resizer/ME7vJ-jxdIzZPwzY8rM3sWSu-kU=/802x1240/arc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com/ap-ne-1-prod/public/SWCGVJNFLODMXKG4U2AGYZEVMU.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fappledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com%2Fresizer%2FME7vJ-jxdIzZPwzY8rM3sWSu-kU%3D%2F802x1240%2Farc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fap-ne-1-prod%2Fpublic%2FSWCGVJNFLODMXKG4U2AGYZEVMU.gif&h=e2d98dab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n防暴警見蘇父拍攝即粗暴喝止（箭嘴示），然後發射四發胡椒球彈。讀者提供圖片<br />\nAppleDaily<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://appledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com/resizer/z-sHZ1d18azV0q1B6UiEm9IYOeI=/802x531/arc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com/ap-ne-1-prod/public/BDETKYTW4OCYMRFLXALGYYBIVE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fappledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com%2Fresizer%2Fz-sHZ1d18azV0q1B6UiEm9IYOeI%3D%2F802x531%2Farc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fap-ne-1-prod%2Fpublic%2FBDETKYTW4OCYMRFLXALGYYBIVE.jpg&h=e8985c22&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n蘇先生談及事件仍感氣憤，憂影響家中長者健康。劉永明攝<br />\nAppleDaily<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://appledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com/resizer/FI07SN4OzDIlE7zaSDqAp8c9_Yo=/802x1069/arc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com/ap-ne-1-prod/public/KZNXUNO5YXJ2UIXDIUB5Z4QMLE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fappledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com%2Fresizer%2FFI07SN4OzDIlE7zaSDqAp8c9_Yo%3D%2F802x1069%2Farc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fap-ne-1-prod%2Fpublic%2FKZNXUNO5YXJ2UIXDIUB5Z4QMLE.jpg&h=41995f32&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n蘇家床褥留有胡椒球彈碎片。<br />\nAppleDaily<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n防暴喝查三年輕人<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：性侵傳聞不絕 女生脫口罩控訴<br />\n<br />\n鏡頭所見，警員喝令該三名年輕人將雙手放在頭上及蹲下受查，有年輕人向警員稱「我哋都冇做乜嘢喎！」隨即被警員喝止，「調查你呀，收聲！」牆角同時傳來一把女子聲音，與警員對罵。警員向她咆哮：「你同我講你有BB嘛，如果返到去唔係嘅，就係誤導警務人員！」<br />\n<br />\n大約一分鐘後，警員發現蘇父正拍攝，隨即喝止：「即刻收部機入返屋，照咩呀你喺度？警告你，唔入返去，用胡椒槍對你。」蘇父心想「呢度係我屋企嚟，點解要收返手機」，防暴警第二次警告，不足一秒即向蘇宅發射兩個胡椒球彈。<br />\n<br />\n蘇先生昨在家中談及此事時仍氣憤難平，「佢哋（防暴警）射咗兩槍胡椒球彈，兩三秒後再射兩個。好彩窗冇爆，但啲碎片同爆啲煙霧吹入嚟，搞到我爸成面都係，成間屋都有，好刺鼻，不停咳同流鼻水」，部份胡椒球彈碎片遺在床上。防暴警開槍後離去，並將三名被截查的年輕人帶走。蘇直斥警方離譜，其父親在家中拍攝並沒有犯法或做錯任何事，「影乜都冇問題㗎」，警員叫收回手機，之後還射胡椒球彈，當時家中除父母還有外婆，擔心胡椒彈影響長者健康。<br />\n<br />\n此外，對於科大生周梓樂離世，蘇先生亦有感而發，「好可惜，一個22歲後生仔，咩原因而走咗唔知，但我覺得同警察脫離唔到關係，警察一定有責任。係喺佢哋所謂執法嘅時間下，令到一個年輕人走咗，係相當有責任」。他又指，「（警察）又講大話，又話冇入停車場，有CCTV影到又話有入。呢個被揭發啫，唔知有幾多冇揭發，收收埋埋」。蘇指想追究警方胡亂發射胡椒球彈，惟「咁多嘢要追究，點排到我吖！」非常無奈。<br />\n<br />\n■記者劉永明"},{"pid":"a5d7b632d9efe9bf9eb2c1b222e76c5ae9e8a87c","tid":1703743,"uid":36722,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T12:01:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21c77e495d10ca5d4bce0ef1be1a62414b0eb17e","tid":1703743,"uid":194560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T12:02:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d15d444133e9b315aca4f840ad83e76209e9da63","tid":1703743,"uid":9315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T12:04:00.000Z","msg":"轉貼： 明刀明槍的示威行動會漸漸消失<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1375656/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1375656/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n講法律已經制衡唔到狗  下下捉住佢地好過分好過分黎講都係清算之時先有用 依刻講完佢地都唔會收斂"},{"pid":"75473adbe0a53c948e51a47868ed4ea6740e6bd2","tid":1703743,"uid":86040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T12:04:18.000Z","msg":"推！ 黑警死全家"},{"pid":"3a9a8464223c5191902d428bed47656a718a7279","tid":1703743,"uid":133341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T12:05:10.000Z","msg":"屌啊"},{"pid":"45f97fdffc02c4d2d32c152727e17f3c3692611d","tid":1703743,"uid":1524,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T12:08:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5152fbe71d5aa22f80944280ba2f47c8c51afbe","tid":1703743,"uid":9315,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"45f97fdffc02c4d2d32c152727e17f3c3692611d","tid":1703743,"uid":1524,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T12:08:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T12:09:34.000Z","msg":"強姦都犯法添  你知我知狗都知<br />\n佢就係知犯法都冇人制衡先犯姐嘛"},{"pid":"0658e85984dad0834f67de0ed879131b10b97e92","tid":1703743,"uid":264866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T12:10:14.000Z","msg":"會唔會遲啲響屋企食飯痾屎都唔得!"},{"pid":"7a28f20dfb88c7e296ab23b8a70f4e8ccdc304bb","tid":1703743,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T12:12:48.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"></span>"}]}